    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80b0-b2d5-efde4b7f6580",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Personalized learning promises an educational experience catered to a student’s knowledge level. To address this, authors believe recommender systems can be very helpful, especially if the feature extraction (creating the student representation) is ontology-based. Thus, they propose a Recommender System for Personalized Learning Sequences in Programming (PSLP). ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80b0-b2d5-efde4b7f6580",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "24b30e64-e269-4370-9ac7-57a1b4389219"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-08T19:44:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-08T19:49:00.000Z",
