    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80ba-a223-ff2a504cbac1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The system includes a knowledge model that is ontology-derived and the recommender has 3 stages based on semantic rules and ontology representation. Testing of the system is done on 32 learners and results show that participants using the system needed less time to find a suitable learning path than students using non-recommender approaches.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80ba-a223-ff2a504cbac1",
        "parent": {
